{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_760.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x21,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "My goodness. Even this boring<CR>paperwork is welcome after what<CR>we just went through."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "How weird is it to be happy to do paperwork?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "The other Linca...said she'll come back again, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Do you think she's really gonna come back?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "For Linca, I am like her other self."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I am sure...she will return."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But given that she's such a calculating individual, experiencing an unexpected result like that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It might be some time before she recalculates everything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Then, we don't have to worry for now? I'm glad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, this may be a silly question,<CR>but...are you and her twins, Linca?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "...There are at least eight of us, including me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "What!? That many!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "There are probably more by now.<CR>It's such a pain to deal with."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Well, if Linca comes back, protect me again, okay Linca?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hey, where's your response?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Marion, do you not regret saving me back then?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x125,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What are you saying all of a sudden!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I have been causing nothing but trouble for you since then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd3,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Simply keeping me close to you is like carrying a bomb."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "My very existence will bring trouble for you in the future."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "So, maybe I should just disappear from..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I'll get mad at you if you say anything more!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Saving you and keeping you by my side were both my decisions. There is nothing for you to worry about."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure Ayesha feels the same way. Right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I'm totally not okay with Linca going away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Besides, I think it's wonderful that you two are together!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "But, as long as I am here, I might bring further danger to you both."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Then, you'll just have to protect us again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Linca, you are strong. And if I say it, it must be true."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "(Linca and the other Linca...<CR>It's a bit confusing, but...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "(Yup. Staying with Marion suits Linca the best!)"
        }
    ]
}